{"tid":2387546,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨參議員Warren去信SEC 要求回覆 究竟對沖基金同Reddit討論 有冇違反證券條例","createTime":"2021-01-30T11:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T15:34:38.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"acb46193550e8e50cd83addf59dc5a8bf2e0f358","tid":2387546,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T11:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kDZ7ju2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkDZ7ju2.png&h=faf659ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.warren.senate.gov/imo/media/doc/01.29.2021%20Letter%20from%20Senator%20Warren%20to%20Acting%20Chair%20Lee.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.warren.senate.gov%2Fimo%2Fmedia%2Fdoc%2F01.29.2021%2520Letter%2520from%2520Senator%2520Warren%2520to%2520Acting%2520Chair%2520Lee.pdf&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjFlQFaTeS91CmK6iy9gpT9M%3D&h=7fb1504e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.warren.senate.gov/imo/media/doc/01.29.2021%20Letter%20from%20Senator%20Warren%20to%20Acting%20Chair%20Lee.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n新聞：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯⋯Warren, a Senate Banking Committee member and 2020 Democratic presidential candidate, wrote that she was concerned about all aspects of the struggle, including Wall Street &ldquo;shorting&rdquo; of stock and the GameStop backlash.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;In addition to GameStop, several other publicly traded companies, including AMC; BlackBerry; Bed, Bath, and Beyond; Nokia; and Tootsie Roll Industries, have seen huge shifts in their share price driven by similar internet trading schemes,&rdquo; Warren wrote.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;These wild fluctuations are just the latest indication that many private equity firms, hedge funds, and other investors, big and small, are treating the stock market like a casino, giving little consideration to the companies, communities, workers, and consumers that may be affected by these risky bets. The recent chaos reveals a clear distortion in securities markets, with benefits accruing to investors that do not clearly benefit the company&rsquo;s workers, consumers, or the broader economy.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nWarren continued, quoting from a Washington Post article, &ldquo;With many of these traders &lsquo;cloaked in anonymity, there is no way of knowing whether messages touting GameStop come from average Joes &ndash; or scam artists executing a &lsquo;pump-and-dump&rsquo; stock scheme.'&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nypost.com/2021/01/29/elizabeth-warren-enters-gamestop-discourse-with-letter-to-sec/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2021%2F01%2F29%2Felizabeth-warren-enters-gamestop-discourse-with-letter-to-sec%2F&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjFlQFaTeS91CmK6iy9gpT9M%3D&h=0fa319c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://nypost.com/2021/01/29/elizabeth-warren-enters-gamestop-discourse-with-letter-to-sec/</a>"},{"pid":"f51ff3257f04482f7ff3ede533508be09320f716","tid":2387546,"uid":150427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T12:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f7de664e6a8099a3edc8f7541505cf14162445","tid":2387546,"uid":267167,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T12:05:44.000Z","msg":"啫係想兩邊各打50大板"},{"pid":"a79977b026962649ce6e9175c2494f26140f23b2","tid":2387546,"uid":150427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"40f7de664e6a8099a3edc8f7541505cf14162445","tid":2387546,"uid":267167,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T12:05:44.000Z","msg":"啫係想兩邊各打50大板"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T12:33:29.000Z","msg":"投機政客<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf3546a3617